        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> Your last action was a successful @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Shove].</p><hr /><p>You leverage your knowledge of energy, mass, and motion against your opponents to manipulate their battlefield positioning. The Shoved creature continues moving. They're pushed back an additional 5 feet, or 10 feet if the required Shove was a critical success. If they would collide with a solid surface due to this movement, you immediately attempt to @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Trip] them as a free action, even if they're no longer within your reach.</p>"
